      "message": "As the command execution doesn\u0027t need swarmingService and taskID, we should move this to main(), renaming this to executeCmd or something?\n\nThe main would look like\n\n```\n...\ncmd, err :\u003d c.createTaskRequestCommand(ctx, taskID, service)\nif err !\u003d nil {\n  ...\n}\n...\nif err :\u003d executeCmd(cmd, w); err !\u003d nil {\n  ...\n}\n```",
